          "text": [
            "<p><strong>QUESTIONS TO ANSWER</strong></p><p>Drag this text tile to the right side of CLUE. Type answers to the questions below!</p><p>Question 1: What makes it difficult to find these signals? </p><p></p><p>Question 2: Describe your process for finding a signal. How long does it take to find one?</p><p></p>"
